Following ref. 52, we calculate the surface buoyancy flux, B, across 16 CMIP6 models using equation (5):5\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
